N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 1000.11 - Assistance with documents

State Regulations

For good cause shown to the presiding examiner (or, if
none, the secretary), the board will reproduce and serve documents filed by
non-applicant municipal and local parties and provide such parties access to
transcripts. Notes
